headline: Equifax Introduces First-in-Market Mortgage Solution that Delivers Credit Report Alongside Employment Status from The Work Number®
summary: Equifax® (NYSE: EFX) has launched a new solution, The Work Number® Report Indicator, enabled by the Equifax Cloud™ to empower lenders by delivering a first in market Equifax credit report with an indicator of employment status earlier in the mortgage qualification process.
